00:00:07,941 --> 00:00:08,742
[ANZAI]

5
00:00:08,842 --> 00:00:09,976
[KANO]
Hello there.

6
00:00:10,076 --> 00:00:11,211
[SAKAKI]
This gentleman is a friend of

