shot Anzai.

15
00:00:32,165 --> 00:00:33,800
But... back there...

16
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:36,670
[ZERO SEVEN]
Don't fight me, and I'll get you
back unharmed.

17
00:00:36,770 --> 00:00:37,971
[TSUKASA]

18
00:00:38,071 --> 00:00:39,072
[ZERO SEVEN]
I really don't want to have to

19
00:00:39,172 --> 00:00:41,107
hurt you. Just do as I say.

20
00:00:41,207 --> 00:00:43,043
[TSUKASA]
