25
00:00:50,817 --> 00:00:52,285
[ZERO SEVEN]
You're a supporter?

26
00:00:52,385 --> 00:00:55,221
[TSUKASA]
I'm not sure about that... I
just uh...

27
00:00:55,321 --> 00:00:56,823
[ZERO SEVEN]
