[ANZAI] <Huh?>
[KANO] You don't think you're
being a little overprotective?

54
00:03:27,307 --> 00:03:28,408
[ANZAI]
I just thought...

55
00:03:28,509 --> 00:03:29,810
I just don't want to have to put

56
