[KANO]
Drinking blood isn't what's
important here.

123
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,803
Different things will work
better for different people.

124
00:06:09,903 --> 00:06:12,338
What happens to you when you
transform?

125
00:06:12,438 --> 00:06:15,441
What situations lead
to a transformation?

126
00:06:15,542 --> 00:06:18,244
You need to have exact answers
to those questions.

127
00:06:18,344 --> 00:06:20,614
So that you're not paralyzed
with fear.

128
00:06:21,414 --> 00:06:22,683
Yanagi has told me...

129
00:06:22,783 --> 00:06:24,551
you're so afraid of transforming

130
00:06:24,651 --> 00:06:27,187
you can't get anywhere near your
lady‐friend.

131
00:06:27,287 --> 00:06:28,188
[ANZAI]
What?

132
00:06:28,288 --> 00:06:29,155
[KANO]
So first, you need

133
00:06:29,255 --> 00:06:30,591
to get to know yourself.

134
00:06:30,691 --> 00:06:34,360
If you want to face your
girlfriend and protect her.

135
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:36,396
There are ways out there that
will enable

136
00:06:36,496 --> 00:06:38,298
you to control your
bloodlust.

137
00:06:38,398 --> 00:06:39,600
