Hospital.

143
00:06:50,811 --> 00:06:52,613
This is a hostage situation.

144
00:06:52,713 --> 00:06:54,581
The hostage is a young woman
with short hair

145
00:06:54,681 --> 00:06:55,916
and a scar across her face.

146
00:06:56,016 --> 00:06:57,083
[ANZAI]

147
00:06:58,919 --> 00:07:01,688
[ZERO NINE]
Okay, we're here, Zero Seven.

148
00:07:01,788 --> 00:07:03,056
[TSUKASA]
I couldn't stop myself

149
00:07:03,156 --> 00:07:04,090
from helping them.

150
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:06,359
Am I just being too naive?

151
00:07:06,459 --> 00:07:08,028
[ZERO SEVEN]
