police scanner.

154
00:07:13,233 --> 00:07:15,435
I'll let you know if anything
starts to happen.

155
00:07:15,536 --> 00:07:18,304
[TSUKASA]
So just what exactly do you
people do?

156
00:07:18,404 --> 00:07:19,573
[ZERO NINE]

157
00:07:19,673 --> 00:07:21,107
[ZERO SEVEN]
Exterminate devils.

158
00:07:21,207 --> 00:07:22,442
[TSUKASA]

159
00:07:22,543 --> 00:07:23,877
[ZERO SEVEN]
This devil issue has been hidden

160
00:07:23,977 --> 00:07:26,547
for years and our mission is to
expose it.

161
00:07:26,647 --> 00:07:30,450
To warn all the people...and
eradicate the problem.

162
00:07:30,551 --> 00:07:32,418
[TSUKASA]
Eradicate!?

163
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,987
[JILL]
Hey! Where are you going?

164
00:07:34,087 --> 00:07:36,289
[ANZAI]
