191
00:08:33,446 --> 00:08:34,948
is the circles under their eyes.

192
00:08:35,048 --> 00:08:39,052
And the devils who drink blood
don't even have those anyway.

193
00:08:39,152 --> 00:08:40,821
[ZERO SEVEN]
You're saying if they drink
blood,

194
00:08:40,921 --> 00:08:44,224
