there?

195
00:08:44,324 --> 00:08:45,225
[ZERO SEVEN]

196
00:08:45,325 --> 00:08:46,126
[ZERO NINE]
Zero Seven!

197
00:08:46,226 --> 00:08:47,528
[ZERO SEVEN]

198
00:08:47,628 --> 00:08:49,029
[ZERO NINE]
