the car you abandoned.

200
00:08:51,932 --> 00:08:53,499
And the GPS for both Zero Six

201
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,435
and Zero Five has just gone
offline.

202
00:08:55,536 --> 00:08:58,739
[ZERO SEVEN]
You were able to turn off our
GPS trackers, right?

203
00:08:58,839 --> 00:09:00,240
[ZERO NINE]

204
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:01,542
