companies

227
00:09:58,098 --> 00:10:01,101
to see if anyone picked up any
injured passengers.

228
00:10:01,201 --> 00:10:03,469
[TSUKASA]
You have people working inside
Division 5?

229
00:10:03,570 --> 00:10:06,306
[ZERO SEVEN]
You're a civilian, the less you
know about this the better.

230
00:10:06,406 --> 00:10:09,142
[TSUKASA]
